<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>
            Lists in the HTML
        </title>
    </head>
    <body>
      <p><b>Name: </b>Ashay Vitthal Patakare</p>
      <p><b>Batch: </b>SYA S3</p>
      <p><b>Experiment: </b>4</p>
        <h1>Lists in the HTML</h1>
        <p>HTML lists organize content using tags like 'ul','ol' & 'li'. They improve readability by presenting data in a structured format. </p>
        <hr>
        <ul><li><h2><em>Ordered Lists</em></h2></li>
        <p> Ordered lists have an inherent order and each item is numbered.</p>
        <h3>Numeric Type</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><i>Cofee</i></li>
            <li><i>Tea</i></li>
            <li><i>Milk</i></li>
        </ol>
        <h3>Alphabet Type</h3>
        <ol type="a">
            <li><i>Diamond</i></li>
            <li><i>Gold</i></li>
            <li><i>Silver</i></li>
            <li><i>Bronze</i></li>
        </ol>
        <hr>
        <li><h2><em>Unordered Lists</em></h2></li>
        <p>Unordered lists have no inherent order and each item is bulleted.</p>
        <h3>Disc Type</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><i>Mars</i></li>
             <li><i>Earth</i></li>
              <li><i>Venus</i></li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Square Type</h3>
        <ul type=square>
              <li><i>AI</i></li>
               <li><i>Gen AI</i></li>
                <li><i>Agentic AI</i></li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Circle Type</h3>
        <ul type=circle>
             <li><i>Dictionary</i></li>
             <li><i>Array</i></li>
             <li><i>Tree</i></li>
             <li><i>Tuple</i></li>
              <li><i>Set</i></li> 
        </ul>
        <hr>
        <li><h2><em>Description Lists</em></h2></li>
        <p>Description lists contain a list of terms and descriptions for each term.</p>
        <dl>
            <dt>HTML</dt>
            <dd>HTML is the standard markup language for Web pages.</dd>
            <dt>CSS</dt>
            <dd>Cascading Style Sheets (CSS) is used to format the layout of a webpage.</dd>
            <dt>Javascript</dt>
            <dd>JavaScript is the programming language of the web.</dd>
        </dl>
<hr>
        <li><h3><b>Nested List</b></h3></li>
         <ol type="A">
            <li><i>Fortron</i></li>
            <ul><li><i>C</i></li>
            <li><i>C#</i></li></ul>
            <li><i>C++</i></li>
        
        <ol type=1 start=5>
            <li><i>Science</i></li>
             <li><i>Commerce</i></li>
              <li><i>Art</i></li>
        </ol>
        </ol>
        </ul>
        <hr>
    </body>
</html>
